Scott: You got to draw a line somewhere.

670
00:43:37,309 --> 00:43:37,731
Rym: But anyway.

671
00:43:37,751 --> 00:43:37,911
Rym: Yeah.

672
00:43:37,932 --> 00:43:39,820
Rym: Well, the line I draw is much more simple.

673
